1️⃣ OSI Model (Final Deep Clarity)
Big Picture Idea

OSI is not just layers → it’s a pipeline of data transformation

Mental Model (Factory 🏭)

Data goes through stages:

Application → user input
Presentation → formatting/encryption
Session → connection
Transport → reliability
Network → routing
Data Link → local delivery
Physical → bits on wire
Why It Works

Each layer:

has one job
can be improved independently
Real Insight (Interview Gold ⭐)

👉 Errors at different layers mean different problems:

Physical → cable issue
Network → routing issue
Transport → packet loss
Memory Trick

OSI = Data processing pipeline

